=== Verb ===
'''to crow''' ([[crowed]], crowed)

# To make the shrill sound characteristic of a rooster, either in joy, gaiety, or defiance.
# To shout in exultation or defiance; to brag.
# To utter a sound expressive of joy or pleasure.

